  "description": "Welcome out-of-town guests with an unforgettable Lake Travis cruise! Perfect for wedding welcome parties with 14-75 guests, professional service, and Austin hospitality. Start your wedding weekend in style with a Lake Travis welcome party cruise! Give your out-of-town guests an authentic Austin experience while bringing everyone together before your big day. The relaxed boat setting helps guests from both sides meet and bond, creating a warm, inclusive atmosphere for your celebration. Professional captain and crew, premium Bluetooth sound for announcements and music, flexible format for mingling and introductions, BYOB or bar service available, large capacity for extended families, Austin skyline and lake views, perfect icebreaker activity, casual yet memorable experience, catering coordination available. Fleet accommodates all sizes: Day Tripper (14 guests, $195/hr), Me Seeks the Irony (25 guests, $295/hr), Clever Girl (50-75 guests, $495/hr). Popular format: 2-3 hour evening cruise. Packages: Standard cruise, Essentials (+$100-200/hr), Ultimate (+$250-350/hr). Book 6-8 weeks ahead for wedding weekend dates.",
